0:01:13.36,000 --> 0:01:15,000
was drawing new maps of the planet,

19
0:01:15.92,000 --> 0:01:16,000
and these maps have now spread,

20
0:01:17.44,000 --> 0:01:19,000
and I'm going to show you one of them now.

