0:07:41.72,000 --> 0:07:45,000
And all of this only became possible

138
0:07:46.92,000 --> 0:07:47,000
within my lifetime

139
0:07:48.72,000 --> 0:07:51,000
to see this is where we are living.

140
0:07:52.64,000 --> 0:07:53,000
We have enough water.

